{"tid":1914231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曹星如似唔似世清","createTime":"2020-03-07T11:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T12:41:40.000Z","uid":234509,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb36ff65b16c23a8d49f85eb1251df210571fbc","tid":1914231,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:40:48.000Z","msg":"打唔贏啲勁人（宇清）<br />\n就笠水 避戰 <br />\n搵埋啲垃圾（佩清）出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係世清語錄：<br />\n宇狗收皮啦 你咸家產都未開到我年啊傻閪<br />\n你係到谷撚住都冇撚用你啖氣忍到下世啦柒頭<br />\n我笠撚硬水 你今世都打唔撚到我架啦<br />\n你買撚曬2020啲場啦傻閪<br />\n屌你老母卜埋場<br />\n比人笑都好過比你打到變豬頭啦傻閪<br />\n突然約隻抽都知你兩手準備 日操夜操想搵我做沙包 你都戇撚鳩<br />\n正所謂 阿婆跑得快 一定有古怪<br />\n150%肯撚定宇狗有練開武嘅<br />\n咁突然搵我隻抽 你當我傻？屌你老味<br />\n比你笑我笠水 你叻囉<br />\n雖然笠水啫 你當我傻架？叫個跑開步從來唔打拳出黎比你打鑊金 你老母生撚左你個腦未 屌你老母"},{"pid":"e40e8b9f252001931ec53097a90dd44e343b5e9b","tid":1914231,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:41:46.000Z","msg":"近排吹緊咩風"},{"pid":"dda05ba099ff785ba4a77e5ace9fa474d273f94d","tid":1914231,"uid":22589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"薯星如明刀明槍呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e1187e2118aef18994e1ad7680a867700172f7","tid":1914231,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda05ba099ff785ba4a77e5ace9fa474d273f94d","tid":1914231,"uid":22589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"薯星如明刀明槍呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"佩清都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a629a4faf65ca96b1cd09ad8241394f9e5dc68","tid":1914231,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda05ba099ff785ba4a77e5ace9fa474d273f